    <item>
      <title>巴西斥资创纪录 80 亿美元遏制卢拉引发的市场崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-market-rout-risks-a-crisis-as-lula-resists-austerity-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着巴西货币暴跌，该国市场多年来首次成为国际关注的焦点，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的高级经济助理们面临着严峻的现实。他们担心，自己无力阻止恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-market-rout-risks-a-crisis-as-lula-resists-austerity-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Archegos 法官拒绝 Bill Hwang 减刑申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bill-hwang-returning-to-court-to-fight-for-less-prison-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官确认了对 Archegos Capital Management 创始人 Bill Hwang 18 年监禁的判决，驳回了有关他应该被允许在家中舒适地度过三分之一刑期的论点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bill-hwang-returning-to-court-to-fight-for-less-prison-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股推动股市上涨；美元缩减涨幅：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员重新评估美联储的政策走向并权衡新的经济数据，美国股市在短暂下跌后恢复上涨。日本央行维持借贷成本不变后，日元继续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 22:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
